28
00:03:26.798 --> 00:03:29.624
<i>Police say the parents.
driven by severe financial hardship.</i>

29
00:03:29.624 --> 00:03:31.073
<i>killed their young son</i>

30
00:03:31.073 --> 00:03:34.259
<i>before taking their own lives.</i>

31
00:03:34.259 --> 00:03:35.957
<i>The room was piled with</i>

32
00:03:35.957 --> 00:03:38.246
<i>overdue bills and scrap paper.</i>

33
00:03:38.246 --> 00:03:40.106
<i>and the family's bank account was</i>

34
00:03:40.106 --> 00:03:42.584
<i>reportedly empty.</i>

35
00:03:42.584 --> 00:03:45.378
<i>The tragedy has sent
shockwaves through society.</i>

36
00:03:45.378 --> 00:03:47.130
<i>as economic hardship</i>

37
00:03:47.130 --> 00:03:50.141
