43
00:05:22.350 --> 00:05:24.352
- Punish them!
- Punish them!

44
00:05:24.352 --> 00:05:27.105
Gojin Chemical.
acknowledge the industrial accident!

45
00:05:27.105 --> 00:05:29.107
- Acknowledge it!
- Acknowledge it!

46
00:05:29.107 --> 00:05:31.776
Gojin Chemical. apologize to the public!

47
00:05:31.776 --> 00:05:33.904
- Apologize!
- Apologize!

48
