You've been through a lot.

62
00:06:06.419 --> 00:06:10.065
Thank you. We're counting on you.

63
00:06:10.065 --> 00:06:12.776
The courts must punish Gojin Chemical!

64
00:06:12.776 --> 00:06:14.778
- Punish them!
- Punish them!

65
00:06:14.778 --> 00:06:17.489
Gojin Chemical.
acknowledge the industrial accident!

66
