103
00:11:07.035 --> 00:11:10.446
The chairman's office is on the 52nd floor.
the Future Strategy Office on the 47th.

104
00:11:10.446 --> 00:11:12.254
Yes. sir.

105
00:11:17.624 --> 00:11:20.103
