- Yes. take this way.

106
00:11:23.960 --> 00:11:25.226
Petty.

107
00:11:25.226 --> 00:11:27.198
Right here.

108
00:11:34.026 --> 00:11:36.352
It's for the chairman only.

109
00:11:36.352 --> 00:11:38.030
Geez.

110
00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:40.373
I don't even have the key.

111
00:11:49.124 --> 00:11:51.543
Let's take a breather.

112
00:11:52.408 --> 00:11:56.080
If we miss even one piece of paper.
we're screwed.

113
00:11:56.080 --> 00:11:58.674
It's fine. Relax.

114
00:11:59.612 --> 00:12:02.281
- Got a cigarette?
- What?

115
00:12:09.391 --> 00:12:12.791
By the way. didn't they say
the prosecutor was a woman?

116
00:12:12.815 --> 00:12:13.920
[30 minutes earlier]

117
00:12:25.683 --> 00:12:28.867
2035-Na-9722.

118
00:12:28.867 --> 00:12:33.247
We will begin the industrial accident
damages trial against Gojin Chemical.

119
00:12:35.288 --> 00:12:37.139
Ms. Han Na Young and
[Han Na Young. Plaintiff from Gojin Chemical]

120
00:12:37.139 --> 00:12:40.828
twenty-four employees who worked at
Gojin Chemical's Yeoju plant...

121
00:12:40.828 --> 00:12:42.559
have been diagnosed with

122
00:12:42.559 --> 00:12:44.584
acute leukemia and brain tumors.

123
00:12:44.584 --> 00:12:45.776
Also.

124
00:12:45.776 --> 00:12:48.635
nine have already died.

125
00:12:48.635 --> 00:12:50.095
All of them were young.

126
00:12:50.095 --> 00:12:52.514
in their twenties or early thirties.

127
00:12:52.514 --> 00:12:54.258
Counsel for the plaintiffs.

128
00:12:54.258 --> 00:12:56.696
do you have anything new
beyond what we already know?

129
00:12:56.696 --> 00:12:57.820
What?

130
00:12:57.820 --> 00:13:00.342
Your Honor.

131
00:13:00.342 --> 00:13:02.192
Gojin Chemical's work sites are

132
00:13:02.192 --> 00:13:03.840
fully sealed to prevent

133
00:13:03.840 --> 00:13:06.996
