134
00:13:12.794 --> 00:13:15.474
Leukemia can develop
from even minimal exposure

135
00:13:15.474 --> 00:13:16.865
to benzene or formaldehyde.

136
00:13:16.865 --> 00:13:19.136
This is just a one-sided claim
by the plaintiffs.

137
00:13:19.136 --> 00:13:21.904
Both sides are noted.

138
00:13:21.904 --> 00:13:23.768
Counsel for the defense.

139
00:13:23.768 --> 00:13:26.269
you filed a motion for an expert opinion

140
00:13:26.269 --> 00:13:29.066
on the link between
Gojin Chemical's work environment

141
00:13:29.066 --> 00:13:30.564
and the workers' leukemia. correct?

142
00:13:30.564 --> 00:13:31.631
Yes.

143
00:13:31.631 --> 00:13:33.283
We recommend

144
00:13:33.283 --> 00:13:35.714
Professor Kim Seok Hyun of Hankuk University

145
00:13:35.714 --> 00:13:38.410
as the court-appointed expert.

146
00:13:44.637 --> 00:13:46.429
<i>We'd like...</i>
[Go Jin Gyu. CEO of Gojin Chemical]

147
00:13:46.429 --> 00:13:49.056
<i>Gwangmin Law Firm to handle the defense.</i>
[Go Jin Gyu. CEO of Gojin Chemical]

148
00:13:49.056 --> 00:13:50.904
<i>Well...</i>

149
00:13:51.536 --> 00:13:53.955
<i>I happen to be the head of Haenal Law Firm.</i>

150
00:13:53.955 --> 00:13:57.468
<i>I'm well aware your son-in-law
is a sitting judge.</i>

151
00:13:57.468 --> 00:13:59.477
<i>Cases he oversees</i>

152
00:13:59.477 --> 00:14:02.332
<i>are often handled by Gwangmin.</i>

153
00:14:02.332 --> 00:14:04.337
<i>a firm Haenal set up under another name.</i>

154
00:14:04.337 --> 00:14:05.645
<i>This trial is...</i>

155
00:14:05.645 --> 00:14:07.818
<i>a matter of life and death
for Gojin Chemical.</i>

156
00:14:07.818 --> 00:14:09.812
<i>Former judges are useful.</i>

157
00:14:09.812 --> 00:14:12.425
<i>but a sitting judge is even better. right?</i>

158
00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:22.896
<i>Gojin Chemical is...</i>

159
00:14:24.133 --> 00:14:27.295
<i>really lucky.</i>

160
00:14:27.295 --> 00:14:28.521
<i>Nine are already dead.</i>

161
00:14:28.521 --> 00:14:31.941
<i>and twenty-four have leukemia.</i>

162
00:14:32.657 --> 00:14:35.557
<i>We agreed on a partial win for the plaintiffs.</i>

163
00:14:35.557 --> 00:14:38.251
<i>so pay a reasonable amount and wrap it up.</i>

164
00:14:38.251 --> 00:14:40.052
<i>Okay.</i>

165
00:14:41.423 --> 00:14:43.157
<i>A partial win for the plaintiffs?</i>

166
00:14:43.157 --> 00:14:44.182
<i>Yes.</i>

167
00:14:44.182 --> 00:14:48.649
<i>As long as it looks like
the company made some effort.</i>

168
00:14:48.649 --> 00:14:50.008
<i>that should be fine.</i>

169
00:14:50.008 --> 00:14:52.327
<i>It'll hurt the company's image.</i>

170
00:14:52.327 --> 00:14:54.062
<i>and sales will drop.</i>

171
00:14:54.062 --> 00:14:56.591
<i>But if the plaintiffs' claims are
dismissed outright.</i>

172
00:14:56.591 --> 00:15:00.163
<i>the blame will fall on the court.</i>

173
00:15:00.163 --> 00:15:03.856
<i>The additional cost is
three hundred million in bearer bonds.</i>

174
00:15:04.876 --> 00:15:06.676
<i>Oh.</i>

175
00:15:07.430 --> 00:15:10.049
<i>You're bolder than your father-in-law.</i>

176
00:15:11.315 --> 00:15:13.781
<i>Send it by courier.</i>

177
00:15:14.484 --> 00:15:16.326
<i>But still.</i>

178
00:15:17.057 --> 00:15:20.000
<i>is this really appropriate for a judge?</i>

179
00:15:24.702 --> 00:15:28.088
<i>That's exactly why I can do this.</i>

180
00:15:42.575 --> 00:15:43.359
[Lee Han Young]

181
00:15:43.359 --> 00:15:45.941
<i>People say he is his in-laws' lapdog.</i>

182
00:15:45.941 --> 00:15:48.243
<i>He is a snake.</i>

183
00:15:50.128 --> 00:15:52.488
<i>There are companies
that chew up their workers.</i>

184
00:15:52.488 --> 00:15:55.415
<i>What's wrong with a judge like this?</i>

185
00:15:58.045 --> 00:15:59.780
The research team's tests show

186
00:15:59.780 --> 00:16:03.350
all hazardous substances
from Gojin Chemical's Yeoju plant

187
00:16:03.350 --> 00:16:06.550
