191
00:16:20.110 --> 00:16:22.148
Well... I can't say

192
00:16:22.148 --> 00:16:25.832
they matched one hundred percent.

193
00:16:25.832 --> 00:16:27.316
But as a researcher.

194
00:16:27.316 --> 00:16:29.427
I took the conditions
at the time into full account

195
00:16:29.427 --> 00:16:30.703
and did my best.

196
00:16:30.703 --> 00:16:34.065
Any errors in the testing
or other possibilities?

197
00:16:34.065 --> 00:16:37.085
Less than one percent.

198
00:17:03.010 --> 00:17:04.119
What's going on?

199
00:17:04.119 --> 00:17:05.261
[Choi Jong Hak.
CEO. S Construction]

200
00:17:05.261 --> 00:17:06.287
What?

201
00:17:06.287 --> 00:17:08.870
Why is the prosecution here?

202
00:17:08.870 --> 00:17:10.670
Damn it.

203
00:17:13.359 --> 00:17:14.594
Sir.

204
00:17:14.594 --> 00:17:15.688
We've got a problem.

205
00:17:15.688 --> 00:17:16.689
- Wait.
- Prosecutors...

206
00:17:16.689 --> 00:17:19.324
You can't just barge in like this.

207
00:17:22.423 --> 00:17:24.181
This is Prosecutor Kim Jin Ah.

208
00:17:24.181 --> 00:17:26.975
from the Special Division of
the Seoul Central Prosecutors' Office.

209
00:17:26.975 --> 00:17:30.802
We're beginning a search
and seizure of S Construction.

210
00:17:41.787 --> 00:17:43.298
Chairman Jang Tae Sik.

211
00:17:43.298 --> 00:17:44.950
<i>this must be quite a shock.</i>

212
00:17:44.950 --> 00:17:46.977
<i>I'm Prosecutor Kim Jin Ah
from the Central District.</i>

213
00:17:46.977 --> 00:17:48.515
<i>Long time no see.</i>

214
00:17:48.515 --> 00:17:50.380
<i>We'll meet soon.</i>

215
00:17:50.380 --> 00:17:53.506
Yeah. soon.

216
00:17:55.640 --> 00:17:56.629
[Search and Seizure Warrant]

217
00:17:56.629 --> 00:17:59.191
I'm out of breath.

218
00:17:59.217 --> 00:18:00.750
[Jang Tae Sik.
Chairman. S Group]

219
00:18:02.862 --> 00:18:05.121
What's the password?

220
00:18:07.474 --> 00:18:08.500
What?

221
00:18:08.500 --> 00:18:10.820
1-1-0-4-5-6.

222
00:18:36.832 --> 00:18:38.531
Mr. Kim Yong Jin.

223
00:18:38.531 --> 00:18:40.552
